#                           the output it produced is kept in evals/scale_pdfs_results.json
#   tab_raw / data_tab    — Text Anonymization Benchmark (third-party ECHR corpus + ground truth);
#                           built by evals/build_tab.py
#   data_scale            — synthetic 1,000-doc set for evals/scale.py
data/pdfs_scale/
tab_raw/
data_tab/
data_scale/
